textTemplates.name: thankYouLabelTextTemplate
textTemplates.text: Thank you for taking the time to give us your feedback.

textTemplates.name: welcome_question_lref_tt
textTemplates.text:
Thank you for using Insight Wellbeing at Work. Your feedback about the help you have received is very important to us. 


We would be most grateful if you would complete this brief questionnaire in order to help us to monitor and improve the counselling service.
